{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-practice-numbers-20-to-99/task-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 1","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada ćeš raditi vežbe brojeva za desetice. Koristi tabelu sa brojevima od 0 do 10 kao referencu. Nećeš koristiti sve.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Number</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kineski</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">0</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>零<rp>(</rp><rt>líng</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>一<rp>(</rp><rt>yī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>二<rp>(</rp><rt>èr</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三<rp>(</rp><rt>sān</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四<rp>(</rp><rt>sì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>五<rp>(</rp><rt>wǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>六<rp>(</rp><rt>liù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">7</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>七<rp>(</rp><rt>qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">8</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>八<rp>(</rp><rt>bā</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">9</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>九<rp>(</rp><rt>jiǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">10</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>十<rp>(</rp><rt>shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ova vežba nema zvuk. Popunite praznine odgovarajućim brojevima za kineski.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Brojevi za desetice na kineskom